# Issue X3-3575 - 2016-09-22 by RICAR : Allow to change the ship from address on transportation notes
# Issue X3-3575
Assign "[M:"+WABRMSK+"]BPANUM" With [F:FCY]FCY
Assign "[M:"+WABRMSK+"]NAM(0)" With [F:FCY]FCYNAM
Assign "[M:"+WABRMSK+"]NAM(1)" With ""
#If WABRMSK="ADB1"
#  If [F:FCY]FCY<>WBPRNUM | [F:FCY]BPAADD<>WBPAADD
