# Issue X3-3575 - 2016-09-22 by RICAR : Allow to change the ship from address on transportation notes
# Issue X3-3575
If WABRMSK = "ADR" and dim([M:ADR1]ADRVAL) > 0
  Assign "[M:"+WABRMSK+"]ADRVAL"  With [F:BPA]ADRVAL
Endif
# End issue X3-3575
